name: Battlesounds
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: battle sounds
des:
With battle sounds, you will experience real war or battle sounds on your Alexa devices.
it has included gun sound, siren, war sounds, etc.
Now we have 50+ different battle sounds available.
for repeating sound user's can say "repeat".
for the next sound user's can say 
give me next, next sound, next etc

if you like it then share and review it so we added more sounds for you.
thanks
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
